their respective owners and is accessed by public API.
<br>
All other content licensed under <a rel="license" href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons Attribution-Share Alike 3.0 License</a>.
</div>

<div> <!-- container -->

<%= javascript_include_tag 'jquery-1.3.2.min' %>
<%= javascript_include_tag 'hoverIntent' %>
<%= javascript_include_tag 'application' %>
<%= javascript_include_tag 'ga'  %>

</body>
</html>